commitResults.messageTitle: removed original code and added Level 0 Greet Functionality
Implement a skeletal version of Duke that starts by greeting the user, simply echos commands entered by the user, and exits when the user types bye.
Changed programe structure to OOP. Add the ability to store whatever text entered by the user and display them back to the user when requested.
Removed Functions class and added Task class. Added the capability to mark tasks as done
Added Javadoc comments and general comments. Tweaked the code a bit to follow coding standard
